<span class='tline' id='l434' data-llen='8982:9009'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0024', 'WYG', '013-37b' );" name="013-37b" class="pb">[013-37b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l435' data-llen='9009:9032'>右圖剝之象曰柔變剛也純乾之卦而柔變之一變為</span>
<span class='tline' id='l436' data-llen='9032:9055'>姤二變為遯三變為否四變為觀五變為剝此變卦見</span>
<span class='tline' id='l437' data-llen='9055:9071'>於易者也陰陽升降變而為六十四</span>
